231
00:18:46,706 --> 00:18:48,083
Pak Lee Won-seok, mari masuk.

232
00:18:48,166 --> 00:18:49,709
Permisi. Maaf.

233
00:18:52,504 --> 00:18:53,421
Pak Kepala.

234
00:18:55,799 --> 00:18:58,218
- Apa yang telah kau perbuat?
- Maaf?

235
00:18:58,301 --> 00:18:59,803
Kau terlibat masalah apa?

236
00:18:59,886 --> 00:19:01,805
Ada masalah apa sampai dia memecatmu?

237
00:19:03,765 --> 00:19:05,600
Direktur Oh, Pak Kepala Joo, Ye Jin-woo.

238
00:19:05,683 --> 00:19:07,852
Mereka bertiga, aku paham.

239
00:19:08,061 --> 00:19:09,437
Tapi kenapa kau juga?

240
00:19:10,146 --> 00:19:10,980
Aku?

241
00:19:11,064 --> 00:19:12,440
Namamu ada di daftar juga.

242
00:19:12,524 --> 00:19:15,568
Presdir bilang dia memecatmu.

243
00:19:16,694 --> 00:19:18,279
Apa yang terjadi?

244
00:19:19,072 --> 00:19:20,573
Apa ulahmu yang membuatnya kesal?

245
00:19:20,657 --> 00:19:23,034
Kenapa dia melampiaskan kemarahannya
kepada kita?

246
00:19:27,539 --> 00:19:28,873
<i>Kematian Lee Jeong-seon?</i>

247
00:19:31,334 --> 00:19:33,962
<i>Kau tak ingin aku menerapkan
bayaran per kinerja.</i>

248
00:19:34,546 --> 00:19:35,547
Tapi Anda

249
00:19:36,339 --> 00:19:38,299
tetap memotong gaji awal perawat.

250
00:19:39,968 --> 00:19:41,678
Bagaimanapun, hasilnya tetap sama.

251
00:19:55,567 --> 00:19:56,609
Si bodoh itu.

252
00:19:57,110 --> 00:19:57,944
YE JIN-WOO

253
00:19:58,027 --> 00:20:00,029
Di mana dia sekarang?

254
00:20:15,044 --> 00:20:17,881
Astaga. Bukankah Anda ibu Dokter Ye?

255
00:20:17,964 --> 00:20:19,257
Ada keperluan apa ke sini?

256
00:20:19,340 --> 00:20:20,592
Apa kabar?

257
00:20:21,342 --> 00:20:23,052
Apakah Jin-woo tidak di sini?

258
00:20:24,846 --> 00:20:26,806
Dia bekerja semalaman.

259
00:20:26,890 --> 00:20:30,059
Dia pasti tertidur di rumah.
Dia tidak menjawab ponselnya.

260
00:20:30,643 --> 00:20:34,230
Astaga. Kenapa dia tidak menjawab
telepon kepala departemennya?

261
00:20:34,856 --> 00:20:35,982
Biasanya dia tak begitu.

262
00:20:37,192 --> 00:20:38,026
Maaf.

263
00:20:38,109 --> 00:20:41,362
Tidak apa-apa. Bukan itu maksudku.

264
00:20:42,780 --> 00:20:45,033
Bukan apa-apa.

265
00:20:46,409 --> 00:20:48,661
Baiklah, Anda pasti sibuk. Sampai jumpa.

266
00:20:48,745 --> 00:20:50,914
Baik. Hati-hati di jalan.

267
00:20:55,418 --> 00:20:56,753
Sial.

268
00:21:37,043 --> 00:21:38,002
Hei, apa kau...

269
00:21:40,046 --> 00:21:40,922
Kau sudah bangun?

270
00:21:41,589 --> 00:21:42,632
Bagus kau sudah bangun.

271
00:21:43,508 --> 00:21:44,634
Makalah lalu tidur lagi.

272
00:21:46,678 --> 00:21:49,222
Kapan Ibu datang?
Seharusnya bangunkan aku saja.

273
00:21:49,430 --> 00:21:50,348
Baru saja.

274
00:21:51,182 --> 00:21:52,892
Kami bahkan tidak memakai ini.

275
00:21:53,518 --> 00:21:54,727
Sudah beres.

276
00:21:57,814 --> 00:21:59,190
Keadaan di RS baik-baik saja?

277
00:22:01,192 --> 00:22:04,946
Terus diberitakan di TV dan koran.

278
00:22:05,446 --> 00:22:06,656
Itu dunia luar.

279
00:22:07,573 --> 00:22:09,575
Kami terlalu sibuk
untuk menyadari semua itu.

280
00:22:09,659 --> 00:22:12,036
Apakah hubunganmu dan Seon-woo
baik-baik saja?

281
00:22:12,120 --> 00:22:13,746
Tentu saja hubungan kami baik.

282
00:22:15,373 --> 00:22:18,251
Katanya dia ingin tinggal sendiri.

283
00:22:20,169 --> 00:22:21,671
Dia mengatakan sesuatu kepadamu?

284
00:22:21,754 --> 00:22:23,631
Itukah alasan kedatangan Ibu?

285
00:22:25,425 --> 00:22:26,384
Tidak mengherankan.

286
00:22:42,567 --> 00:22:45,153
Seon-woo mengirim surel.

287
00:22:46,863 --> 00:22:47,739
Kepada Ibu?

288
00:22:49,449 --> 00:22:51,492
Terkadang dia sangat sentimental.

289
00:22:55,913 --> 00:22:56,914
Dia bilang apa?

290
00:22:58,791 --> 00:22:59,709
Dia bilang...

291
00:23:02,170 --> 00:23:04,297
kecelakaan waktu itu adalah kesalahannya.

292
00:23:06,049 --> 00:23:08,217
Dia bilang ayahmu meninggal karena dia.

293
00:23:11,512 --> 00:23:12,764
Padahal itu salah ibu

294
00:23:13,264 --> 00:23:14,766
karena mengabaikannya.

295
00:23:15,641 --> 00:23:17,143
Ibu bilang itu demi kebaikannya.

296
00:23:19,479 --> 00:23:21,147
Selama bertahun-tahun ini...

297
00:23:24,901 --> 00:23:27,945
Ibu tidak tahu itu sangat membebaninya.

298
00:23:30,948 --> 00:23:34,327
Tapi jika ibu mengakuinya sekarang
dan bilang bahwa ibu tahu

299
00:23:35,286 --> 00:23:37,371
dan kau juga tahu,

300
00:23:38,623 --> 00:23:40,208
dia pasti takut

301
00:23:41,167 --> 00:23:43,544
bahwa kita membenci dia

302
00:23:45,088 --> 00:23:46,506
selama ini.

303
00:23:54,972 --> 00:23:56,432
Aku akan bicara dengannya

304
00:23:57,433 --> 00:23:58,684
agar dia tak merasa begitu.

305
00:24:12,281 --> 00:24:15,243
Saat Seon-woo bilang dia ingin pindah,

306
00:24:17,120 --> 00:24:18,204
ibu pikir

307
00:24:19,205 --> 00:24:21,666
mungkin karena kau menemukan seseorang.

308
00:24:21,749 --> 00:24:23,126
Siapa yang kutemui dan di mana?

309
00:24:23,209 --> 00:24:24,627
Aku memilih tidur jika sempat.

310
00:24:24,710 --> 00:24:28,047
Bagaimana dengan seseorang di rumah sakit?

311
00:24:28,131 --> 00:24:31,134
Tidak ada siapa pun di RS.
Hanya ada orang-orang seperti No-eul.

312
00:24:34,887 --> 00:24:35,888
Ibu.

313
00:24:36,389 --> 00:24:38,307
Aku tak akan melakukan itu
kepada Seon-woo.

314
00:24:38,391 --> 00:24:39,392
Aku tidak mengencani No-eul.

315
00:24:41,310 --> 00:24:42,895
Lagi pula,

316
00:24:42,979 --> 00:24:45,314
walau Ibu membuangku dan No-eul
ke pulau terpencil,

317
00:24:45,398 --> 00:24:47,233
kami cuma akan sibuk berburu.

318
00:24:47,692 --> 00:24:49,026
Kami akan berebut makanan.

319
00:24:51,404 --> 00:24:52,530
Sebaiknya ibu pergi.

320
00:24:53,531 --> 00:24:54,365
Tapi...

321
00:24:54,866 --> 00:24:57,493
Ibu bekerja terus.
Seon-woo pulang sebentar lagi.

322
00:24:58,369 --> 00:24:59,537
Tidak apa-apa.

323
00:25:00,913 --> 00:25:02,331
Ibu harus pulang lebih awal.

324
00:25:02,415 --> 00:25:04,417
Awalnya, ibu tidak berencana
mampir ke sini.

325
00:25:05,960 --> 00:25:07,295
Aku akan antar Ibu pulang.

326
00:25:08,838 --> 00:25:11,674
Ibu naik mobil.
Mau antar ke area parkir saja?

327
00:25:14,010 --> 00:25:15,011
Putraku.

328
00:25:15,428 --> 00:25:16,554
Astaga.

329
00:25:32,111 --> 00:25:32,987
Ibu.

330
00:25:34,322 --> 00:25:35,239
Baik.

331
00:25:35,740 --> 00:25:39,118
Kau bisa flu. Kenakan sesuatu.

332
00:25:39,368 --> 00:25:40,912
Aku bisa mati kegerahan.

333
00:25:43,831 --> 00:25:47,001
Tetap saja. Sebaiknya kau pakai jaket.

334
00:26:26,499 --> 00:26:28,668
<i>Tidak bisa kubayangkan
bagaimana perasaan Ibu,</i>

335
00:26:30,002 --> 00:26:32,964
<i>betapa takut dan bingungnya Ibu saat itu.</i>

336
00:26:34,590 --> 00:26:35,633
<i>Seingatku,</i>

337
00:26:36,968 --> 00:26:38,970
<i>ketika Ayah meninggal,</i>

338
00:26:39,762 --> 00:26:41,264
<i>Ibu seusiaku sekarang.</i>

339
00:26:44,475 --> 00:26:46,936
<i>Seharusnya Ibu tidak menderita
di usia semuda itu.</i>

340
00:26:48,271 --> 00:26:50,231
<i>Seharusnya kami melepas Ibu saat itu.</i>

341
00:26:52,858 --> 00:26:54,652
Ibu harus memasak begitu tiba di rumah?

342
00:26:55,361 --> 00:26:56,279
Tidak.

343
00:26:56,862 --> 00:26:59,031
Pasangan tua seperti kami
jarang masak sendiri.

344
00:26:59,115 --> 00:27:02,493
Orang yang lebih tua dari Ibu
bisa tersinggung jika mendengarnya.

345
00:27:04,078 --> 00:27:04,996
Begitukah?

346
00:27:09,208 --> 00:27:10,418
<i>Aku sadar jauh setelahnya</i>

347
00:27:12,086 --> 00:27:13,921
<i>bahwa Ibu sedang dalam masa keemasan</i>

348
00:27:14,964 --> 00:27:16,632
<i>saat menjadi orang tua tunggal.</i>

349
00:27:19,927 --> 00:27:21,345
<i>Ibuku, yang mendorong</i>

350
00:27:22,555 --> 00:27:23,764
<i>dan menarikku,</i>

351
00:27:25,641 --> 00:27:28,686
<i>seorang pria dewasa,
ke sekolah kedokteran di puncak bukit</i>

352
00:27:30,563 --> 00:27:31,522
<i>berulang-ulang kali.</i>

353
00:27:36,193 --> 00:27:37,778
<i>Ibu selalu menungguku</i>

354
00:27:38,279 --> 00:27:40,323
<i>di lorong sekolah yang dingin.</i>

355
00:27:42,617 --> 00:27:44,201
<i>Kenapa begitu mudah aku berpikir</i>

356
00:27:44,702 --> 00:27:46,203
<i>Ibu baik-baik saja?</i>

357
00:27:48,289 --> 00:27:49,373
<i>Jika kupikirkan lagi...</i>

358
00:27:50,791 --> 00:27:52,376
<i>aku jadi frustrasi</i>

359
00:27:53,169 --> 00:27:55,463
<i>karena ternyata aku bodoh
dan kekanakan-kanakan.</i>

360
00:28:05,473 --> 00:28:06,349
Hei.

361
00:28:12,897 --> 00:28:14,523
<i>Jangan berpikir Ibu menelantarkanku.</i>

362
00:28:16,901 --> 00:28:17,818
<i>Aku mohon,</i>

363
00:28:18,778 --> 00:28:19,987
<i>jangan merasa bersalah.</i>

364
00:28:26,952 --> 00:28:28,245
<i>Aku anak manja yang berpikir</i>

365
00:28:29,038 --> 00:28:30,373
<i>hanya aku yang terluka.</i>

366
00:28:31,290 --> 00:28:34,335
<i>Aku tak mengatakan apa-apa di luar,
tapi berteriak dan marah</i>

367
00:28:35,461 --> 00:28:36,879
<i>hanya saat di rumah.</i>

368
00:28:39,965 --> 00:28:42,551
<i>Ibu mendedikasikan
setiap hari dalam hidup Ibu</i>

369
00:28:43,469 --> 00:28:44,804
<i>dan seluruh masa muda Ibu</i>

370
00:28:45,971 --> 00:28:47,515
<i>untukku.</i>

371
00:28:49,892 --> 00:28:51,435
<i>Siapakah di dunia ini</i>

372
00:28:52,019 --> 00:28:54,522
<i>yang mampu menyayangiku
seperti Ibu menyayangiku?</i>

373
00:29:01,946 --> 00:29:03,656
Astaga.

374
00:29:04,657 --> 00:29:06,117
Bu.

375
00:29:06,200 --> 00:29:07,034
Halo.

376
00:29:07,118 --> 00:29:08,536
Ya, halo.

377
00:29:08,619 --> 00:29:09,954
Apa kabar?

378
00:29:10,037 --> 00:29:12,206
Kabar baik, terima kasih.
Bagaimana dengan Anda?

379
00:29:12,289 --> 00:29:13,332
Ya, kabarku baik.

380
00:29:14,125 --> 00:29:16,001
Kau pasti ingin bertemu anak-anakmu.

381
00:29:16,085 --> 00:29:17,378
Aku membawa makanan.

382
00:29:17,461 --> 00:29:18,504
Begitu rupanya.

383
00:29:19,797 --> 00:29:21,257
- Biar aku bawa.
- Tidak perlu.

384
00:29:33,978 --> 00:29:35,688
<i>Ada yang perlu kuceritakan.</i>

385
00:29:38,190 --> 00:29:42,236
<i>Adakalanya aku berharap Paman Bo-hun
memberi tahu Ibu untukku.</i>

386
00:29:44,321 --> 00:29:47,616
<i>Tapi dia tidak akan menceritakan
hal yang dia dengar saat konsultasi.</i>

387
00:29:53,038 --> 00:29:54,123
<i>Dan karena...</i>

388
00:29:55,416 --> 00:29:57,334
<i>dia sudah tidak bersama kita lagi,</i>

389
00:29:59,003 --> 00:30:00,504
<i>aku yang harus memberi tahu Ibu.</i>

390
00:30:01,505 --> 00:30:02,423
<i>Ibu.</i>

391
00:30:05,718 --> 00:30:07,344
<i>Aku tak bisa langsung memberi tahu</i>

392
00:30:08,095 --> 00:30:09,013
<i>dan setelahnya,</i>

393
00:30:10,306 --> 00:30:12,099
<i>aku tidak sanggup menceritakannya.</i>

394
00:30:14,226 --> 00:30:15,436
<i>Jin-woo tidak tahu.</i>

395
00:30:15,519 --> 00:30:16,437
SURAT PENERIMAAN

396
00:30:16,645 --> 00:30:19,732
Sayang, aku mengirim putra kita
ke sekolah kedokteran.

397
00:30:20,691 --> 00:30:21,734
Usahaku bagus, bukan?

398
00:30:23,152 --> 00:30:25,529
Kau sangat bangga kepadaku, bukan?

399
00:30:30,743 --> 00:30:34,163
NAMA: YE JIN-WOO
SEKOLAH KEDOKTERAN

400
00:30:36,582 --> 00:30:38,167
<i>Akulah yang melakukan itu</i>

401
00:30:39,627 --> 00:30:40,628
<i>terhadap Ayah.</i>

402
00:30:41,420 --> 00:30:42,338
<i>Kecelakaan itu...</i>

403
00:30:44,423 --> 00:30:45,424
<i>adalah kesalahanku.</i>

404
00:31:01,023 --> 00:31:02,441
<i>Ayah menyuruhku berhenti.</i>

405
00:31:04,652 --> 00:31:06,111
<i>Ayah melarangku main di mobil.</i>

406
00:31:07,488 --> 00:31:08,364
<i>Tapi...</i>

407
00:31:09,532 --> 00:31:10,449
<i>aku...</i>

408
00:31:21,210 --> 00:31:22,086
<i>Aku pelakunya.</i>

409
00:31:23,420 --> 00:31:25,172
<i>Aku merebut Ayah dari hidup Ibu.</i>

410
00:31:27,091 --> 00:31:31,178
<i>Dia, yang merupakan suami Ibu
dan ayah Jin-woo.</i>

411
00:31:35,349 --> 00:31:36,183
<i>Ibu.</i>

412
00:31:37,893 --> 00:31:40,479
<i>Tolong jangan kasihani aku.</i>

413
00:31:41,814 --> 00:31:42,815
<i>Kelumpuhanku adalah</i>

414
00:31:43,941 --> 00:31:45,067
<i>hukuman yang pantas.</i>

415
00:32:13,470 --> 00:32:15,014
<i>Dia bilang ingin hidup sendiri.</i>

416
00:32:15,890 --> 00:32:18,559
<i>Aku melihat kalian bersama.
Aku dan Seon-woo.</i>

417
00:32:27,026 --> 00:32:30,654
ZIGBANG

418
00:32:30,738 --> 00:32:33,824
DAFTAR RUMAH YANG DISEWAKAN

419
00:32:38,454 --> 00:32:40,164
- Sedang apa?
- Kau tidak tidur?

420
00:32:43,500 --> 00:32:45,127
Kau berniat pindah?

421
00:32:46,211 --> 00:32:48,172
Tidak, aku hanya melihat-lihat.

422
00:32:52,885 --> 00:32:53,802
Tidurlah di kamarmu.

423
00:32:53,886 --> 00:32:56,388
Aku besok sif malam.
Aku bisa tidur sepanjang siang.

424
00:32:57,514 --> 00:32:58,599
Baik.

425
00:33:04,229 --> 00:33:05,105
<i>Jadi, karena itu...</i>

426
00:33:22,706 --> 00:33:24,083
17 PANGGILAN TIDAK TERJAWAB

427
00:33:24,166 --> 00:33:27,503
PAK KEPALA LEE DONG-SU, NONA KIM,
PARK JAE-HYEOK

428
00:33:30,422 --> 00:33:31,590
PAK KEPALA LEE DONG-SU

429
00:33:34,635 --> 00:33:36,011
Hai, Pak Kepala...

430
00:33:36,095 --> 00:33:37,930
Kenapa baru menelepon sekarang?

431
00:33:38,180 --> 00:33:39,807
Aku sudah suruh jangan mencolok.

432
00:33:40,391 --> 00:33:42,393
- Apa?
<i>- Kau pasti senang</i>

433
00:33:42,476 --> 00:33:44,520
<i>tidak perlu kena omelanku lagi.</i>

434
00:33:44,603 --> 00:33:48,190
Kenapa kau harus melibatkan diri
dan terjebak kekacauan ini, Bodoh?

435
00:33:48,983 --> 00:33:49,858
Sekarang bagaimana?

436
00:33:50,859 --> 00:33:52,486
Tidak kena omelan lagi bagaimana?

437
00:33:53,821 --> 00:33:55,906
Terserah! Bertindaklah sesukamu.

438
00:34:02,413 --> 00:34:03,622
Kenapa dia...

439
00:34:13,215 --> 00:34:14,675
Aku pulang sekarang.

440
00:34:17,386 --> 00:34:18,345
Dokter Lee.

441
00:34:20,222 --> 00:34:21,223
Mau minum denganku?

442
00:34:23,267 --> 00:34:24,393
Aku harus pergi.

443
00:34:33,569 --> 00:34:35,237
Mana mungkin dia mau minum?

444
00:34:44,538 --> 00:34:45,831
Kau mau pulang?

445
00:34:46,790 --> 00:34:48,042
Ya.

446
00:34:55,340 --> 00:34:56,300
Nona Kang.

447
00:34:57,342 --> 00:34:59,303
Ya? Aku?

448
00:35:00,095 --> 00:35:02,014
Kau mau minum denganku?

449
00:35:02,931 --> 00:35:03,891
Apa?

450
00:35:10,606 --> 00:35:11,732
Ayo.

451
00:35:14,693 --> 00:35:15,736
Bersulang.

452
00:35:23,202 --> 00:35:24,161
Seperti ini.

453
00:35:24,870 --> 00:35:26,038
Begini cara menutup hari.

454
00:35:27,081 --> 00:35:28,040
Kau jarang minum?

455
00:35:28,540 --> 00:35:30,584
Aku mau minum bersama siapa?

456
00:35:30,709 --> 00:35:31,543
Pak Gu?

457
00:35:33,670 --> 00:35:36,423
Aku "manajer tim", tapi tak ada
yang bisa diajak makan malam.

458
00:35:41,345 --> 00:35:46,141
Tapi biasanya Pak Gu baik.

459
00:36:00,072 --> 00:36:02,282
Sudah berapa lama kau bekerja dengannya?

460
00:36:03,367 --> 00:36:05,410
Sekitar lima atau enam tahun.

461
00:36:06,370 --> 00:36:08,747
Dia masuk ke departemen tempatku bekerja

462
00:36:08,831 --> 00:36:11,959
dan saat dipindah ke Logis,
